@MillionaireMoneyMoves is The Real Deal Millionaire and that’s why we are excited to have him on as our first contributor to the @blackmillionaires_ platform !
.
Cedric Nash is a serial entrepreneur who  became a millionaire making what he has coined “Millionaire Money Moves M$M”. His mission is to help other Black people reach destination millionaire as well as create and maintain wealth through shifting mindset, entrepreneurship and real estate. His approach is unfiltered, unedited and unapologetic.

Follow @millionairemoneymoves if you’re serious about your millionaire journey and stay tuned for what’s next.
